      "side": 1,
      "message": "to be clear: there is a bug currently that if there is a line that exceeds scanner buffer size (which defaults to 64KB), then scan.Err() will return bufio.ErrBufferFull, but it is a separate bug from [invalid pipe handling]. We need to fix it (perhaps in a separate CL), and this change isn\u0027t fixing it. I read a bit of bufio.Scanner and it seems like we have to switch from bufio.Scanner to something else (https://screenshot.googleplex.com/57J88QvBS2RepK7), which again is a larger change and seems unrelated to the fix in this CL.",
